Rating: 3
This was good! The sauce certainly has a flavor you either like or don't like but my husband and I thoroughly enjoyed it. We plan to try it again, backing off a little bit on the cumin to see if it balances the flavors a little more evenly. Have some bread to catch the extra sauce! Yum!

