Yeah, so, this was not good. There are many good steak options, but this is not one to bother with

Rating: 3
Very good indeed. This one had the family going back to the pan with bread to mop up every last drop of the sauce. The only variation I introduced was to slice the steaks diagonally across the vein and trim off some fat (AFTER cooking), then dress the steak slices with the sauce. Overall not spectacular, but definitely a keeper.